comments.body:
Thanks for reaching out, @akostadinov!

Given Podman and it's sibling projects Buildah, Skopeo and CRI-O (to an extent) are subject to such races (as they sync via the file system), I do not think there is much we can do.  The cost of synchronising on this specific use case outweigh the benefits IMHO.

@rhatdan WDYT?
